Enum LengthUnit

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<LengthUnit>
      • com.kamontat.code.unithouse.LengthUnit
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Unit, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<LengthUnit>

    public enum LengthUnit
extends java.lang.Enum<LengthUnit>
implements Unit
    The collection of Length unit.
    Default unit is Meter(m)

    This has 3 different kind of Length
    1) Metric
    2) American System of Measures
    3) Thai unit

    Created by kamontat on 21/4/59.
